# Office Printer 9K

Office Printer 9K is a one-screen dark comedy browser management game built with Phaser 3.

Core fantasy:
- The player is an abused sentient office printer.
- The fantasy is survival under impossible corporate demands.
- The tone is dry, absurd, bureaucratic, and increasingly desperate.

Scope constraints:
- Keep the project small and jam-friendly.
- One main gameplay scene.
- 4 supporting scenes max: Boot, Title, Game, Results.
- Use data-driven content.
- Do not add complex subsystems unless requested.

Always prefer:
- Clear state updates
- Readable UI
- Small reusable content objects
- Short flavor text with strong punch